        {
            "title": "德國稱美國放鬆對俄羅斯石油的制裁是錯誤的",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國總理弗里德里希·默茨批評美國放鬆對俄羅斯制裁、試圖通過暫時允許俄羅斯出售石油來緩解伊朗戰爭引發的油價壓力這一決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普政府已經再一次發出許可證，允許買家接收已在海上的俄羅斯石油，此舉擴大了上周給予印度的臨時豁免範圍。此舉引發烏克蘭盟友擔憂，認為克里姆林宮可能從能源價格飆升中受益，並有更多資金為持續四年的對烏克蘭戰爭提供支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">默茨周五在與挪威首相約納斯·加爾·斯特勒共同舉行的新聞發布會上表示：「讓我說得非常清楚：我們認為現在出於任何原因放鬆制裁都是錯誤的。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7fe29ce6-4f1f-3110-a070-fa9079cd6f7d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位德國保守派領導人表示：「我們將而且必須繼續加大對莫斯科的壓力。我們不會允許伊朗戰爭讓我們因此退縮或分心。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Germany Says US Wrong to Ease Oil Sanctions Against Russia (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ott Ummelas.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BE%E9%AC%86%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E7%9A%84-123026482.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 21:15:13",
